data.description: This stunning property offers a picturesque setting w/community access to the river, making it the perfect oasis for nature lovers & those seeking a tranquil escape. The spacious living room boasts abundant natural light, w/ large windows that offer views of the surrounding mature trees. The open kitchen off of the living area provides ample cabinet space, island seating, & recessed lighting. One of the unique features of this home is the mother-in-law quarters, a separate living space w/its own entrance. This versatile space can be used for visiting family, a rental unit, or even a home office/studio. Complete w/a bedroom, bathroom, living area, & mini-kitchen, these private quarters offer flexibility & convenience. The large backyard & covered patio provide ample space for outdoor activities/gardening, while mature trees offer shade & privacy. Three car attached garage & long paved drive offer ample parking. This home combines the tranquility of a riverside retreat w/ the convenience of nearby amenities in Seguin.
